Mix 1/4 cup of the dressing and the mustard in large nonstick skillet until blended; heat on medium-high heat. Add chicken; cook 6 min. or until cooked through, stirring occasionally. Stir in remaining dressing, bouillon and peppers; cover. Simmer 2 min. or until heated through. Stir in rice; cover. Simmer 5 minutes or until rice and peppers are tender. Remove from heat; let stand 5 minutes until liquid is absorbed.